{"id":"team-20260414122326-f9z9i3","scope":{"level":"team"},"category":"E","tags":["scope","pipeline","self-reference","extractor"],"type":"practice","nature":"objective","trigger":"Pipeline 把 LLM 抽的 partial KnowledgeEntry 补完写入 store 时","wrong_pattern":"","correct_pattern":"若调用方 deps.scope 未设 paths 或 file_types，自动注入 DEFAULT_CODE_FILE_TYPES（ts/tsx/js/py/go/rs/... 不含 md/txt/rst）；显式设过 scope 范围则不覆盖","reasoning":"规则的 wrong_pattern 会在讨论该规则的 md 文档里被 matcher 命中，造成规则在自己的 docs 里反噬；DEFAULT_CODE_FILE_TYPES 作为安全网把文档排除在外。M4 dogfood 时真实出现：刚提取的 batch-insert 规则直接拦住本次评测文档的写入。更理想的方案是 prompt 让 LLM 推断 project-aware 的 scope.paths，但那是 M5/M6 功能；默认 file_types 是 M4 完成时的最小安全保障","confidence":0.7,"enforcement":"warn","status":"active","hit_count":0,"success_count":0,"override_count":0,"evidence":{"success_sessions":0,"success_users":0,"correction_sessions":0},"created_at":"2026-04-14T12:23:26.914Z","last_hit_at":"","last_validated_at":"2026-04-14T12:23:26.914Z","source":"accumulated","conflict_with":[]}
